      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.1333332936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "小美山愛、現地に到着しましたー！\n日本とは空気も違いますね、ワクワクします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8666666825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5333332936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく楽しみで昨日はなかなか寝付けなくて……\nでも飛行機でぐっすり寝たので元気一杯です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2000000159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　しっかり寝てるじゃないか、って？　あはは\nそういえばそうですね、お陰で体調はバッチリです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6666666825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.8666666269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "今日はこの国の、とある村のお祭りに突撃します！\nさっそく村に向かって出発しまーす！　突撃～、GO！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0666666825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.1999997616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "移動と入りの撮影、お疲れ様\n愛の元気が伝わってくる、期待の膨らむ画だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.031338048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざ日本から来てくれて、ありがとうございます\nさっきの収録も、観ていてくれたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8980042617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "愛こそ、LizNoirの海外ツアーと、海外ロケ\n両立お疲れ様。疲れてないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.0634244521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "全然！　{user}さんのお顔を見たら\n元気になりました。この調子で頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9404836874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3326.1829793000074,
          "startTime": 67.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12426.182979300002,
          "startTime": 76.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.9300911188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　見て下さい、{user}さん\nスタッフさんが、何か慌ててるみたいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9300906658,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8236.5760009,
          "startTime": 79.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本当だ。何かトラブルでもあったのかな\nちょっと確認してくるから、待っててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666664124,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3712.064607900004,
          "startTime": 82.2787310203
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.012063392
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……すまん、愛！　俺を許してくれ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0787310203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.7191392024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、急になんですか！？\nまさかお祭りが中止になったとか、トラブルですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2858049075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4191392024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今回の仕事、先方は愛のそっくりモノマネ芸人の\n『大美山ラブ』さんに依頼をしたつもりらしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2416377366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.1914975245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　よくこの番組に出てるラブさん！？\nまさか……飛行機から降りてきた私を見て……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5707380473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8914975245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "今さっき間違いに気付いたってことですか！？\n不肖小美山、芸能人生初の珍事です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3581632296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "完全に俺のミスだ！　俺のバカ！\nなんで今の今まで気付かなかったんだ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.4914750814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「BIG4のアイドルなので無茶振りは控えて下さい」\nと伝えたら、「まるで本物ですね」と言われたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2281040252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "「ツアーがあるので体力的に無理のないように」\nと伝えたら「地方巡業中でしたね」と返されたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6220604369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.6308772803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん……間違いとも言い切れない絶妙な返し……\nこれは仕方ないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4308763187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.0308793148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私はやる気満々でここに来てるんです\n何も問題ありませんよ、続行しましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.6975450199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.3308793148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "怒って、ないのか？　全力でサポートすると\n言っておきながら、こんな間抜けなミスをした俺を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9666826886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "怒りませんよ、私がやりたいと言った仕事ですから\nむしろ間違えてくれたお陰で出られるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.2300393741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.563373669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_13_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "実は私、大美山ラブさんが体を張って\n頑張っているのを見て、元気をもらっていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.8967060407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_airport-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "airport-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.463373669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
